content:
Configure Date Variables in Salesforce Einstein Discovery:

On the Model Settings page, click a date field. The variable panel appears.
In the Alerts tab, respond to any suggestions regarding data issues for this field.

In the Settings tab, configure the following settings:
Transform: Optionally select how to analyze dates by Group by Day of Week or Group by Month of Year.
Include Only: Restrict the date range to include in the analysis by changing the start and end dates.
Histogram: A graph shows the number of values that occur across the range of dates.

Changes take effect after you create the model.
title: Configuring Date Variables in Salesforce Analytics
